; 10月16日
在10月16日上午1時，即此颱風進入菲律賓的警告範圍時，第一個警告隨即發出<ref>[http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/282558/juan-intensifies-enters-rp-area 'Juan' Intensifies, Enters RP Area | The Manila Bulletin Newspaper Online<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。據報當地認為此颱風可能與2009年嚴重破壞當地的[[颱風凱莎娜_(2009年)|颱風凱薩娜]]一樣，會引起超大量的大雨<ref>[http://www.manilastandardtoday.com/insideNews.htm?f=2010/october/16/news2.isx&d=2010/october/16 Manila Standard Today - Megi may dump as much rain as Ondoy - 2010/october/16<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> <ref>[http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/282528/typhoon-juan-sighted-near-north-luzon Typhoon 'Juan' Sighted Near North Luzon | The Manila Bulletin Newspaper Online<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。當地的[[红十字会与红新月会国际联合会|紅十字會]]已預料由於其越來越接近呂宋，故會在當地造成嚴重破壞；此外，亦已預備好在有需要時緊急撒離<ref>[http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/282486/red-cross-ready-new-typhoon Red Cross Ready for New Typhoon | The Manila Bulletin Newspaper Online<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。[[菲律宾大气地球物理和天文管理局|菲律賓大氣地球物理和天文管理局]]已發出公眾的警告信號，並預料將在10月18日登陸<ref>[http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/282466/typhoon-juan-expected-make-landfall-monday-pagasa Typhoon 'Juan' Expected to make Landfall on Monday – PAGASA | The Manila Bulletin Newspaper Online<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>，並將每小時更新颱風動態。已告知[[伊莎貝拉省|伊莎貝拉省]]和[[卡加延省|卡加延省]]的農民，要求他們在星期一以後不要出海釣魚，直到颱風登陸離開，才能回到海上工作。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/regions/view/20101016-298078/Northern-Luzon-prepares-for-Juan |title=Northern Luzon prepares for 'Juan' - INQUIRER.net, Philippine News for Filipinos<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101021033347/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/regions/view/20101016-298078/Northern-Luzon-prepares-for-Juan |archive-date=2010-10-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

10月16日晚上，菲律賓總統呼籲公私營團體合作，令傷亡人數達至最低<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/nation/view/20101016-298066/Aquino-appeals-for-cooperation-ahead-of-storm |title=Aquino appeals for cooperation ahead of storm - INQUIRER.net, Philippine News for Filipinos<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101020182445/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/nation/view/20101016-298066/Aquino-appeals-for-cooperation-ahead-of-storm |archive-date=2010-10-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

; 10月17日
10月17日自從數以百計的民眾知悉鮎魚進一步增強和逼近之後，便開始離開家園<ref>[http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5g15Xe_ymcMjqcGPA7yXaakqsHOjw?docId=5de9c902d1ee4c2bad580a9a0db81cb0 The Associated Press: Strong storm heads for Philippines; thousands flee]</ref>，同時當地亦發出三號風暴信號<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/nation/view/20101017-298206/Typhoon-Signal-no-3-over-Cagayan-Isabela-several-islands |title=Metro Manila, south Luzon now within range of ‘Juan’ - INQUIRER.net, Philippine News for Filipinos<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101020003417/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/nation/view/20101017-298206/Typhoon-Signal-no-3-over-Cagayan-Isabela-several-islands |archive-date=2010-10-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，雖然政府已準備好應對此颱風，但數以千家的家庭亦繼續同時撤離<ref>[http://www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=621754&publicationSubCategoryId=200 (UPDATE) Thousands of families evacuated as typhoon Juan nears | Home >> Other Sections >> Breaking News<!-- Bot generated title -->]{{Dead link|date=2019年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2010-10/17/c_13561519.htm Philippines ready to face super typhoon Megi<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。超過18個省市已經警告此致命的颱風將會接近當地<ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2010/10/17/3040495.htm?section=justin Typhoon Megi storms towards Philippines - ABC News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation)<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>，而[[卡加延省|卡加延省]]已率先在10月17日開始吹強風<ref>[http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/regions/10/17/10/juan%E2%80%99s-strong-winds-now-being-felt-cagayan 'Juan’s' strong winds now being felt in Cagayan | ABS-CBN News | Latest Philippine Headlines, Breaking News, Video, Analysis, Features<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。當天稍後時間，所有官立學校學院已宣佈停課<ref>[http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/282714/typhoon-juan-update-classes-suspended-region-12-and-car Classes Suspended in Region 1,2 and CAR due to Typhoon "JUAN" | The Manila Bulletin Newspaper Online<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。[[菲律宾大气地球物理和天文服務管理局|菲律宾大气地球物理和天文服務管理局]]亦於同日當地下午對受影響人數多於700萬人的地方發出四號風暴信號<ref>[http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/10/17/10/juan-barrels-toward-northern-luzon Powerful 'Juan' barrels toward northern Luzon | ABS-CBN News | Latest Philippine Headlines, Breaking News, Video, Analysis, Features<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/282738/typhoon-juan-growing-stronger Typhoon "JUAN" Growing Stronger | The Manila Bulletin Newspaper Online<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。

在接近登陸之時，其強烈雨帶已開始橫過[[呂宋|呂宋]]，造成山洪暴發。有一人在10月18日下午於[[土格加勞|土格加勞]]被淹死<ref>[http://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/breaking-news/one-dead-as-super-typhoon-megi-hits-philippines/story-e6frf7jx-1225940248838 One dead as super-typhoon Megi hits Philippines]</ref>。

