]{{Dead link|date=2019年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>、山體滑坡<ref name="hill1" />。超過1000名市民因颱風造成船隻[[擱淺|擱淺]]而被困，同時再多兩人受傷<ref>[http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/282811/more-1000-stranded-due-typhoon-juan More than 1,000 stranded due to Typhoon "Juan" (Megi) - Manila Bulletin]</ref>，另外當地的紅十字會派出water search and rescue隊伍到[[卡加延省|卡加延省]]進行搶救行動<ref>[http://www.reliefweb.int/rw/rwb.nsf/db900sid/SNAA-8AC5AF?OpenDocument Philippines: PRC sends Wasar Team to Cagayan - ReliefWeb]</ref>。

